{"tid":879611,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"皮膚差拎入 因為皮膚差搞到冇曬動力","createTime":"2018-10-28T06:11:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-12T00:42:35.000Z","uid":209172,"like":35,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"3a0736a1b70c10f8072e7db9df57d144f2dd6551","tid":879611,"uid":209172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T06:11:25.000Z","msg":"小弟成日覺得自己皮膚差 比唔上其他人<br />\n因為皮膚差搞到冇曬自信 雖然自己有女朋友 但都覺得自己配唔上佢 好唔開心我心裏面好大壓力 明明有能力做到嘅嘢因為皮膚搞到抑鬱冇動力做 之前真係有抑鬱過但係依家又發作 好想喊呀 有冇人可以幫下我"},{"pid":"74c5c53537f4b7d49475bcfa9cc0780971ca6d8c","tid":879611,"uid":209172,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T06:14:55.000Z","msg":"連登有愛 幫下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"232b528e9673d2b8e17d54ec1d6d1c27029da71d","tid":879611,"uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T06:22:21.000Z","msg":"唔好養貓"},{"pid":"79f9245c1c0c993c7a6004636b08fd6cf7ea8c38","tid":879611,"uid":209172,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"232b528e9673d2b8e17d54ec1d6d1c27029da71d","tid":879611,"uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T06:22:21.000Z","msg":"唔好養貓"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T06:29:37.000Z","msg":"唔得阿 佢係我第二個陪伴者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"387afc5e91624a21029102c66b9ce5a416c843f7","tid":879611,"uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79f9245c1c0c993c7a6004636b08fd6cf7ea8c38","tid":879611,"uid":209172,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"232b528e9673d2b8e17d54ec1d6d1c27029da71d","tid":879611,"uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T06:22:21.000Z","msg":"唔好養貓"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T06:29:37.000Z","msg":"唔得阿 佢係我第二個陪伴者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T06:34:00.000Z","msg":"有一個仲唔夠？貪心"},{"pid":"ed414a6d80790bf8bf71f2e7116d3513e0021530","tid":879611,"